{"tid":1332034,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"寫game 一般自學定出去上堂學？","createTime":"2019-07-19T07:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T13:00:13.000Z","uid":8377,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f853a2ad9a7921184e973350db36d8d3f37cac7e","tid":1332034,"uid":8377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:08:22.000Z","msg":"大學好似冇咩科 係有教game engine ,寫script. <br />\n我自己有自學Unity , 都係跟佢個官網既tutorial 同外國既youtube 教學。<br />\n自己本身都有programming 底，<br />\n而家叫做識寫基本既2D game。<br />\n<br />\n諗住遲下學埋Unreal 同 寫VR。<br />\n但發覺自學好似進度有d慢， 主要原因我覺得係網上d教學參差不齊，d 教學又唔完整，要自己左揾右揾 沒一個完整配套guide 住我。<br />\n<br />\n如果有d完整既project 畀我跟住寫 一路學 ，有人guide 住，我覺得學得會快好多。<br />\n<br />\n所以想問下你地學寫game 係咪都係自學<br />\n定還是出去出邊學 例如fevaworks, 又或者一d high dip咁。"},{"pid":"619044cb249d8751795795f03336c4ec45e0b750","tid":1332034,"uid":8377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:12:45.000Z","msg":"另外想問下<br />\n有冇人有考過unity 個d certificate?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個d certificate 對揾想關遊戲開發既工有冇幫助？<br />\n我見好多遊戲開發既工 unity等<br />\n都冇特別要求咩大學咩科同學歷咁。<br />\n<br />\n咁考呢d certificate 會唔會有幫助？ 定還是自己落手落腳寫隻game出黎 會有用d?"},{"pid":"d6e67ef90917e2bf10ff89b03bf395ece8c81473","tid":1332034,"uid":249170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:58:28.000Z","msg":"緊係做多幾隻game 好<br />\n僱主應該睇portfolio 多個睇certificate<br />\n當然兩者都有更好，二選一緊係portfolio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學就緊係去youtube或udemy (10US)學<br />\n<br />\nudemy果d都算有人guide 住你做完整project <br />\n<br />\n有野卡住可以去unity forum 問，英文唔算太差d外國人都會知你講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecdc9c528d67e9294aa4eb522773bbfbd26f8d51","tid":1332034,"uid":131120,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:43:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"615d665f7b34cbb9e8730532179f3b331487f757","tid":1332034,"uid":79869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:58:07.000Z","msg":"真係唔需要讀書<br />\n要讀就讀下algorithm<br />\n自學已經多resources 到你睇唔晒<br />\n如果你想要寫一隻高質Game就更加唔係一個人可以有時間去完成<br />\n你可能會自學覺得慢<br />\n但點為之快？<br />\n其實多數人缺既係實作經驗<br />\n想快好簡單，就係平日習慣試作各種類型Game<br />\n磨練各種技術<br />\n到有idea既時候就可以快速參考舊作，整到新Game"},{"pid":"b1b4b6322cae7eae449ef900f2106f1be1cd6624","tid":1332034,"uid":8377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecdc9c528d67e9294aa4eb522773bbfbd26f8d51","tid":1332034,"uid":131120,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:43:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:14:02.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過去日本發展<br />\n你朋友起香港寫左幾多年game?<br />\n又係自學？"},{"pid":"67eccad1bec0cc750bb31ed4770829bbed12f869","tid":1332034,"uid":131120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:16:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1a99a5ed872fe13ff17a0b5948ee42bc33f07e1","tid":1332034,"uid":8377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6e67ef90917e2bf10ff89b03bf395ece8c81473","tid":1332034,"uid":249170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:58:28.000Z","msg":"緊係做多幾隻game 好<br />\n僱主應該睇portfolio 多個睇certificate<br />\n當然兩者都有更好，二選一緊係portfolio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學就緊係去youtube或udemy (10US)學<br />\n<br />\nudemy果d都算有人guide 住你做完整project <br />\n<br />\n有野卡住可以去unity forum 問，英文唔算太差d外國人都會知你講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:18:47.000Z","msg":"我有上過udemy d unity course呀<br />\