d":79869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:58:07.000Z","msg":"真係唔需要讀書<br />\n要讀就讀下algorithm<br />\n自學已經多resources 到你睇唔晒<br />\n如果你想要寫一隻高質Game就更加唔係一個人可以有時間去完成<br />\n你可能會自學覺得慢<br />\n但點為之快？<br />\n其實多數人缺既係實作經驗<br />\n想快好簡單，就係平日習慣試作各種類型Game<br />\n磨練各種技術<br />\n到有idea既時候就可以快速參考舊作，整到新Game"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"Algorithm其實都係即揾即有<br />\n整Game同寫文差唔多<br />\n都係我手寫我心啫<br />\n<br />\n文筆可能要磨練十年八年<br />\nCoding唔係太爛真係乜都寫得出<br />\n唔識再去學，想寫Platformer咪學少少Physics"},{"pid":"520ea1255bd1ce5189b9237957b266b35d552753","tid":1332034,"uid":131120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aeae0aa1ddbfc2297396c269bfeffaa09d6ab49d","tid":1332034,"uid":8377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"520ea1255bd1ce5189b9237957b266b35d552753","tid":1332034,"uid":131120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:09:29.000Z","msg":"邊度有junior 入場券<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想入<br />\n<br />\n見親好多都要求有experienced"},{"pid":"6e28bd6e2fb568c3898c3791f185c4834492c22e","tid":1332034,"uid":131120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:30:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edbb2a0211fedb9098694ecedb40d2d214d47b97","tid":1332034,"uid":70485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:29:19.000Z","msg":"坦白講<br />\n唔好寫indie<br />\n寫 mod, 儲fan base<br />\n改到咁上下先將個遊戲模式做indie<br />\n當中個技術用到先學，無用就唔好放太多時間<br />\n多D去 indie forum 認識下唔同人<br />\n<br />\n唔好所有野自己做，要outsource<br />\n買assets pack , 搵人寫script<br />\n呢D都好重要<br />\n<br />\n好多近代長久大作都係由mod 改出來<br />\n去到真係做獨立遊戲之前<br />\n個模式已經係改過好多次<br />\n<br />\n做indie唔係只得寫code, 細拆係有3個position<br />\ngraphic , development, game design<br />\n一個人係無可能做得曬一隻大作<br />\n做出來多數都會放棄其中一part<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ntldr: 寫mod (warcraft 3/ starcraft 2/ minecraft/ gta / fallout / skyrim / source engine ...) ,儲fan base, 做prototype, 最後先到implement standalone indie"},{"pid":"617cccec93b4de03943f9cab9fbfa5bc0d7a7cbd","tid":1332034,"uid":70485,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"edbb2a0211fedb9098694ecedb40d2d214d47b97","tid":1332034,"uid":70485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:29:19.000Z","msg":"坦白講<br />\n唔好寫indie<br />\n寫 mod, 儲fan base<br />\n改到咁上下先將個遊戲模式做indie<br />\n當中個技術用到先學，無用就唔好放太多時間<br />\n多D去 indie forum 認識下唔同人<br />\n<br />\n唔好所有野自己做，要outsource<br />\n買assets pack , 搵人寫script<br />\n呢D都好重要<br />\n<br />\n好多近代長久大作都係由mod 改出來<br />\n去到真係做獨立遊戲之前<br />\n個模式已經係改過好多次<br />\n<br />\n做indie唔係只得寫code, 細拆係有3個position<br />\ngraphic , development, game design<br />\n一個人係無可能做得曬一隻大作<br />\n做出來多數都會放棄其中一part<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ntldr: 寫mod (warcraft 3/ starcraft 2/ minecraft/ gta / fallout / skyrim / source engine ...) ,儲fan base, 做prototype, 最後先到implement standalone indie"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86aa70160869ad2ca2e7ffd623460f0d1867a7bb","tid":1332034,"uid":106641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:57:08.000Z","msg":"寫game其實算唔算multimedia同設計成份&gt;programming"},{"pid":"924c798e91887e85c8826e477ce5f6f8c1f2ceca","tid":1332034,"uid":249170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86aa70160869ad2ca2e7ffd623460f0d1867a7bb","tid":1332034,"uid":106641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:57:08.000Z","msg":"寫game其實算唔算multimedia同設計成份&gt;programming"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:40:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得吸唔吸引到人玩你隻game一定係靠graphic同effect等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係私人公司做game graphic designer 下場真係過做雞慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人工同一般graphic designer同價或更低，但門檻要求超級非常高, 同埋每日返工近乎通頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49661c212d7dd1021516d93dd1d6f464b2208e96","tid":1332034,"uid":118709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:37:20.000Z","msg":"香港人8蚊買隻whatsapp都屌哂鬼<br />\n儘早放棄"},{"pid":"1719ebcd569c7f2d8c42630c3a0e65eb416db6ff","tid":1332034,"uid":131120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T23:56:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff217a4f4e37a45c4ea3cdcac1aead69b5d95028","tid":1332034,"uid":79869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86aa70160869ad2ca2e7ffd623460f0d1867a7bb","tid":1332034,"uid":106641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:57:08.000Z","msg":"寫game其實算唔算multimedia同設計成份&gt;programming"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:26:05.000Z","msg":"其實咩都要識...甚至包埋寫作、心理學"}]}